  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/3051",
  "title": "Move from DevNovel to Storybook",
  "body": "In the next major release Storybook (v4 still in alpha) will support [HTML application](https://github.com/storybooks/storybook/blob/master/docs/src/pages/basics/guide-html/index.md). It can be a good opportunity to move our showcase from [DevNovel](https://github.com/algolia/dev-novel) to Storybook to leverage the community & plugins of Storybook. It also brings consistency across our different flavours since React & Vue are already on Storybook. \r\n\r\nRelated https://github.com/algolia/angular-instantsearch/issues/226",
